window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Who will stand in this new world of magic and technology...and who will fall?</p> <p>The end of the world comes as a surprise, and as one world ends, another begins. Transformed by a magical apocalypse that ends civilization as we know it, Astrid awakens in a world filled with monsters, magic, and the remains of modern technology. Together with other survivors, she will have to find her family and figure out how to survive in this new world.</p>"; 
